steps.name: I am on the Capella Home page "https://www.capella.edu/"
"ASK A QUESTION" Menu link available on Home Page Header
I click on ask a question menu
I should see the "Schedule Consultation" link under the menu
I click on ask a schedule consultation link
I should see the schedule consultation modal pop up form
"Nursing" as Area of Study in form
I should see unrestricted RN license question provided to user
